Olympics is the biggest atheltics competition that brings about all the countries in the world¶

The Analysis will dig deeper to find out how the medals distribution has been since the inception of the competition¶

We shall be looking and trying to answer the below¶

  1. The most successful countries
  2. Most sucessful athletes
  3. Best attended fields
  4. Gender representation

Data files will be athletes infromation and NOC contries¶

*Analysis will we performed using the python langauge with libaries of choice including

Pandas - Data manipulation

Matplotlib - Visualization

Seaborn - Visualization

    1. Olympics is a huge competition and over the years, this event has entertained me and even made me appreciate sports in general and as well take the journey to exrecise and pull few kilometres every new week.¶
    2. Sports is what pull the community together, we have seen instances where the community and even the entire country rally behind their own.¶
    3. The data has uncovered alot in terms of how the countries have faired and as well the most successfully athletes in the selected disciplines.¶
    4. Exploratory analysis is the start of some much, focus is to now dig the various features and make interesting conclusions, the various disciplines calls on alot of exercise but also there are other things that data can helps to uncover.¶
